### Get all caches
GET https://diamond-insights.up.railway.app/api/v1/cache
Accept: application/json

### Delete a specific cache
DELETE https://diamond-insights.up.railway.app/api/v1/cache/get-users
Accept: application/json

### Delete all caches
DELETE https://diamond-insights.up.railway.app/api/v1/cache
Accept: application/json